                        <roleName type="rep" corresp="pe__kunigunde_QGW_II_I_1183"><add>anstatt</add></roleName></rs> und <rs type="person" ref="pe__margarethe_QGW_II_I_1183">Margret, seine <roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__friedrich_sleiffer_QGW_II_I_1183">Hausfrau</roleName>
